# Assets Holding Debt Securities Amount

## identifier
de14712

## status
Standard

## type
undefined

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, for reporting entities holdings of debt securities as well as own issues of debt securities. Holding of debt securities comprise claims in all negotiable debt instruments. These are transferable instruments evidencing a relationship of indebtedness. This item is in accordance with accounting standards

## guidance
undefined

